trans-unit.source: Provides information about a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> control that you can display in a catalog of Web Parts controls without having to create an instance of the control.
trans-unit.target: Innehåller information om en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> kontroll som du kan visa i en katalog med webbdelar kontroller utan att behöva skapa en instans av kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: When <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> controls are displayed in a catalog of controls that users can add to a page, some basic information about each control is required.
trans-unit.target: När <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>kontroller visas i en katalog med kontroller som användarna kan lägga till en sida, grundläggande information om varje kontroll krävs.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: For example, it is useful to have a title for the control, and a description, so that as users view a catalog they have enough information to decide whether to add a control to the page.
trans-unit.target: Det är till exempel praktiskt att ha en rubrik för kontrollen och en beskrivning, så att användarna visa en katalog har tillräcklig information för att bestämma om du vill lägga till en kontroll på sidan.

trans-unit.source: However, a catalog of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> controls can potentially contain many controls, and it could affect the performance of an application if an instance of every <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control must be created to extract the information to display in the catalog.
trans-unit.target: Men en katalog med <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>kontroller kan innehålla många kontroller och det kan påverka prestanda för ett program om en instans av varje <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>control måste skapas för att extrahera information som visas i katalogen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: The WebPartDescription class exists so that it is not necessary to create an instance of a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control to retrieve the information about the control that is displayed in a catalog of controls.
trans-unit.target: Klassen WebPartDescription finns så att det inte är nödvändigt att skapa en instans av en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>kontroll för att hämta information om den kontroll som visas i en katalog med kontroller.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: In the Web Parts control set, a WebPartDescription object is also used in conjunction with the various <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> controls when a page is in catalog display mode.
trans-unit.target: Ett WebPartDescription-objekt används i uppsättningen webbdelar kontrollen också tillsammans med de olika <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>kontroller när en sida i katalogen visningsläge.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>

trans-unit.source: The WebPartDescription class has two overloads of its constructor, one that takes a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control as a parameter when an instance is available (the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription.%23ctor%2A> constructor), and one that takes several strings with information about the control as parameters (the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription.%23ctor%2A> constructor).
trans-unit.target: WebPartDescription klassen har två överlagringar av sin konstruktor som tar en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>kontroll som en parameter när en instans som är tillgängliga (det <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription.%23ctor%2A>konstruktor), och ett som tar flera strängar med information om kontrollen som parametrar (den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription.%23ctor%2A>konstruktor).</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription.%23ctor%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription.%23ctor%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: The WebPartDescription class also has several properties designed to contain the description information for <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> controls.
trans-unit.target: WebPartDescription klassen har också flera egenskaper som är avsedda att innehålla information om tabellbeskrivningen <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>kontroller.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: The following table summarizes the WebPartDescription properties, and what property each one corresponds to in a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control.
trans-unit.target: I följande tabell sammanfattas WebPartDescription egenskaper och vilken egenskap en motsvarar i en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: |Description property|Related part control property| |--------------------------|-----------------------------------| |<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription.ID%2A>|<xref:System.Web.UI.Control.ID%2A>| |<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription.Title%2A>|<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.Part.Title%2A>| |<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription.Description%2A>|<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.Part.Description%2A>| |<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription.CatalogIconImageUrl%2A>|<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.CatalogIconImageUrl%2A>|
trans-unit.target: | Beskrivningsegenskapen | Relaterade del kontrollegenskap | |--------------------------|-----------------------------------| | <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription.ID%2A>| <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.ID%2A>| | <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription.Title%2A>| <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.Part.Title%2A>| | <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription.Description%2A>| <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.Part.Description%2A>| | <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription.CatalogIconImageUrl%2A>| <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.CatalogIconImageUrl%2A>|</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.CatalogIconImageUrl%2A></xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription.CatalogIconImageUrl%2A></xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.Part.Description%2A></xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription.Description%2A></xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.Part.Title%2A></xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription.Title%2A></xref:System.Web.UI.Control.ID%2A></xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription.ID%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the class when a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> control instance is available.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av klassen när ett <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> kontroll instansen är tillgänglig.

trans-unit.source: The WebPartDescription constructor is used for creating a new <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription> object based on an existing <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control.
trans-unit.target: Konstruktorn WebPartDescription används för att skapa en ny <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription>objekt baserat på en befintlig <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription>

trans-unit.source: This constructor simply calls the other overload, the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription.%23ctor%28System.String%2CSystem.String%2CSystem.String%2CSystem.String%29> constructor, obtaining the required parameter values from properties on the `part` parameter.
trans-unit.target: Den här konstruktorn anropar bara andra överlagring den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription.%23ctor%28System.String%2CSystem.String%2CSystem.String%2CSystem.String%29>konstruktor, hämta nödvändiga parametervärdena egenskaper på den `part` parameter.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription.%23ctor%28System.String%2CSystem.String%2CSystem.String%2CSystem.String%29>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> control whose information is contained in a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> kontroll vars information finns i en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The property of part is or an empty string ("").
trans-unit.target: Den egenskapen för part är eller en tom sträng ("").

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the class by using several strings that contain description information for a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av klassen med hjälp av flera strängar som innehåller information om tabellbeskrivningen en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> kontroll.

trans-unit.source: The WebPartDescription constructor is used to create a new instance of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription> class when a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control is not available.
trans-unit.target: Konstruktorn WebPartDescription används för att skapa en ny instans av den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription>klass när en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>kontrollen är inte tillgänglig.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription>

trans-unit.source: For example, this occurs in the case of an <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ImportCatalogPart> control when it imports a description file for a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control.
trans-unit.target: Det uppstår till exempel för en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ImportCatalogPart>styr när det importerar en beskrivningsfil för en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ImportCatalogPart>

trans-unit.source: It gets the information it needs to create a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription> object directly from the description file, and a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> instance is not present.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar den information som behövs för att skapa en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription>objekt direkt från beskrivningsfil och en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>instansen finns inte.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription>

trans-unit.source: The value to assign to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription.ID*>.
trans-unit.target: Värdet för att tilldela <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription.ID*>.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription.ID*>

trans-unit.source: The value to assign to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription.Title*>.
trans-unit.target: Värdet för att tilldela <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription.Title*>.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription.Title*>

trans-unit.source: The value to assign to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription.Description*>.
trans-unit.target: Värdet för att tilldela <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription.Description*>.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription.Description*>

trans-unit.source: The value to assign to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription.CatalogIconImageUrl*>.
trans-unit.target: Värdet för att tilldela <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription.CatalogIconImageUrl*>.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription.CatalogIconImageUrl*>

trans-unit.source: id or title is or an empty string ("").
trans-unit.target: ideller title är eller en tom sträng ("").

trans-unit.source: Gets a URL containing the path to an image used as an icon for a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar en URL som innehåller sökvägen till en bild som används som en ikon för en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> kontroll.

trans-unit.source: The CatalogIconImageUrl property corresponds directly to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.CatalogIconImageUrl%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen CatalogIconImageUrl motsvarar direkt till den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.CatalogIconImageUrl%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.CatalogIconImageUrl%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: If that property is set on a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control, then the property in the corresponding <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription> object will also have a value.
trans-unit.target: Om egenskapen är inställd på en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>kontroll och egenskapen i motsvarande <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription>objekt måste även ha ett värde.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: The CatalogIconImageUrl property applies only when a page is in catalog display mode, and a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control is being displayed in a catalog of controls.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen CatalogIconImageUrl gäller bara när en sida är i katalogen visningsläge och en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>kontrollen visas i en katalog med kontroller.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: If the control has an icon assigned to it in the property value, the icon appears in the catalog next to the control.
trans-unit.target: Om kontrollen har en ikon som tilldelats i egenskapsvärdet, visas ikonen i katalogen bredvid kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: A string that contains a URL; the default value is an empty string ("").
trans-unit.target: En sträng som innehåller en URL-Adressen. Standardvärdet är en tom sträng ("").

trans-unit.source: Gets the text of a description for a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar texten i en beskrivning för en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> kontroll.

trans-unit.source: The Description property corresponds directly to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.Part.Description%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen Description motsvarar direkt till den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.Part.Description%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.Part.Description%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: If that property is set on a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control, then the property in the corresponding <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription> object will also have a value.
trans-unit.target: Om egenskapen är inställd på en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>kontroll och egenskapen i motsvarande <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription>objekt måste även ha ett värde.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: The Description property applies only when a page is in catalog display mode, and a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control is being displayed in a catalog of controls.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen beskrivning gäller bara när en sida är i katalogen visningsläge och en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>kontrollen visas i en katalog med kontroller.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: If the control has a description assigned to it, the description appears in the catalog as a ToolTip on the control.
trans-unit.target: Om kontrollen har en beskrivning som tilldelats, visas beskrivningen i katalogen som en knappbeskrivning på kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: A string that contains the description for a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> control; the default value is an empty string ("").
trans-unit.target: En sträng som innehåller beskrivningen för en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> kontroll; standard värdet är en tom sträng ("").

trans-unit.source: Gets the ID of a corresponding <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar ID för en motsvarande <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> kontroll.

trans-unit.source: The value of the ID property cannot be `null`; it must always have a value.
trans-unit.target: Värdet för egenskapen ID får inte vara `null`; det alltid måste ha ett värde.

trans-unit.source: The ID property corresponds directly to the <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.ID%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property.
trans-unit.target: ID-egenskapen motsvarar direkt till den <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.ID%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.UI.Control.ID%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: The ID property applies only when a page is in catalog display mode, and a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control is being displayed in a catalog of controls.
trans-unit.target: ID-egenskapen gäller bara när en sida är i katalogen visningsläge och en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>kontrollen visas i en katalog med kontroller.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: A string that contains the ID of the control.
trans-unit.target: En sträng som innehåller ID för kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: Gets the title text of a corresponding <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar rubriktexten på en motsvarande <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> kontroll.

trans-unit.source: The value of the Title property corresponds directly to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.DisplayTitle%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property.
trans-unit.target: Värdet för egenskapen Rubrik motsvarar direkt till den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.DisplayTitle%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.DisplayTitle%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Whatever the corresponding <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control has for its <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.DisplayTitle%2A> property, that becomes the value of the Title property; otherwise, the title is a calculated value.
trans-unit.target: Det motsvarande <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>kontrollen har för dess <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.DisplayTitle%2A>egenskap, som blir värdet på egenskapen Rubrik; annars rubriken är ett beräknat värde.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.DisplayTitle%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: The Title property applies only when a page is in catalog display mode, and a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control is being displayed in a catalog of controls.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen rubriken gäller bara när en sida är i katalogen visningsläge och en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>kontrollen visas i en katalog med kontroller.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: Whatever title is assigned to a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control appears next to the control in the catalog.
trans-unit.target: Rubriken som är tilldelad till en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>kontrollen visas bredvid kontrollen i katalogen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: A string that contains the title of the corresponding control.
trans-unit.target: En sträng som innehåller namnet på motsvarande kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: The default value is a calculated string supplied by the .NET Framework.
trans-unit.target: Standardvärdet är en beräknad sträng som tillhandahålls av .NET Framework.
